JenkinsAgent.
==============
Jenkins controller administer the job,pipelines,UI credentials.
Jenkins agent execute the build steps.
Jenkins agent we can scale horizontally.
Any type of machine that can run java can be a jenkins agent.


Create an agent node in jenkins
===============================

known hosts file
=================
client----------------------ssh---------server
(Known hosts)
The known hosts file contains all the finger print of the public keys of the remote machines.
When the keys dont match than the client machine shows promt that the host is unknown.
The finger print of the public keys are stored in ~/.ssh/known-hosts file.
When we connect to remote machine the known-hosts file is searched to match the public key finger print presented by the remote machine.




